{"div":{"@":{"xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","type":"article","xml:id":"MG-1700-01_010","resp":"wordpro"},"#":[{"head":{"value":"[Sur la Statue Equestre du Roy]*","id":"/div/#[0]/head"}},{"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", janvier 1700 [tome 1], p. 10-12.","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/#"}}},{"p":{"value":"Les Muses de Virgile sont plus œconomes. Cet illustre Poëte ayant une occasion de loüer Auguste, le fait en deux Vers que la Cour du Prince &amp; le Senat de Rome admirérent.","id":"/div/#[2]/p"}},{"quote":{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nocte pluit totâ, redeunt spectacula manè,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Divisum imperium cum Jove Cæsar habet.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jupiter inonde la nuit.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La pluye en est continuelle,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et Cesar le jour embellit","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De spectacles qu’il renouvelle.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}}},{"p":{"#1":{"value":"Comme je suis ","id":"/div/#[4]/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Andini cultor vatis","id":"/div/#[4]/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":", je me conforme avec peu de vers à son exemple. Ainsi un seul Distique Latin fait ses honneurs à la Statuë Equestre du Roy.","id":"/div/#[4]/p/#2"}}},{"quote":{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Pro Equestri Statuâ.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Effigies regis reginâ spector in Urbe,","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ære gerens Magni Lodoici fortia facta.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}}]}}},{"p":{"value":"En voicy l’explication.","id":"/div/#[6]/p"}},{"quote":{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Statuë auguste, effort de mains habiles,","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’attire les regards de la Reine des Villes,","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et pour rendre immortel le grand Nom de LOUIS,","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mon Bronze s’est chargé de ses faits inoüis.","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}}}]}}